          <td>类型（7.0+已废弃）</td>
          <td>Table</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>Shard</td>
          <td>分片，数据的最小单元</td>
          <td>Partition</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>Replica</td>
          <td>副本，分片的复制</td>
