        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">文档集合：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Doc1: &#34;Java is a programming language&#34;
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Doc2: &#34;Python is also a programming language&#34;
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Doc3: &#34;Java and Python are popular&#34;
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">正向索引（文档 → 词）：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Doc1 → [Java, is, a, programming, language]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Doc2 → [Python, is, also, a, programming, language]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Doc3 → [Java, and, Python, are, popular]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">倒排索引（词 → 文档列表）：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Java         → [Doc1, Doc3]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Python       → [Doc2, Doc3]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">programming  → [Doc1, Doc2]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">language     → [Doc1, Doc2]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">is           → [Doc1, Doc2]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">popular      → [Doc3]
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">...</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
